katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span> is a prime number, any interger a is coprime to p:</p>\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mfrac><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></msup><mo>≡</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">{</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.3600em\" columnalign=\"left left\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>1</mn></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mspace></mspace><mspace width=\"0.6666666666666666em\"/><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">o</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mtext> </mtext><mtext> </mtext><mi>p</mi><mtext> (if exist </mtext><mi>x</mi><mtext> such that </mtext><mi>a</mi><mo>≡</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mtext> )</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mspace></mspace><mspace width=\"0.6666666666666666em\"/><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">o</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi></mrow><mtext> </mtext><mtext> </mtext><mi>p</mi><mtext> (if not exist </mtext><mi>x</mi><mtext> such that </mtext><mi>a</mi><mo>≡</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mtext> )</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a ^ {\\frac{p-1}{2}} \\eq